\section{Managing Accounts Payable}
There are several factors that a company should consider as guidelines for effectively managoing its accounts payable, including:
\begin{itemize}
  \item Financial organization's centralization.
  \item Number, size, and location of vendors.
  \item Trade credit and cost of borrowing or alternative cost.
  \item Control of disbursement float (the amount of time between a check issuance and the check clearing).
  \item Inventory Management (JIT, MRP, etc..)
  \item E-Commerce and Electronic Data Interchange (EDI). 
\end{itemize}
\hfill \\

